{"tid":1810512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<襲警> 防暴警小巴「串燒」撞3車 觀塘繞道最少4人傷","createTime":"2020-01-04T02:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:44:13.000Z","uid":227801,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7ced62d7cf69b89776de275441b3d9345aff45fe","tid":1810512,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:52:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200104/60449050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F60449050&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=c1fbc622\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F60449050&h=96593c7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200104/60449050</a><br />\n<br />\n早上近10時，觀塘繞道西行線麗港城對開，有警方的防暴小巴與3車「串燒」相撞，包括兩部的士及一部貨車。一名的士司機、一名女乘客及兩名防暴警受傷，要送院治理。受事故影響，觀塘繞道出旺角方向交通擠塞，龍尾至觀塘警署對開。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，載有一批水馬的貨車沿中線西行，切到快線期間碰到的士。尾隨貨車的防暴警車連忙扭軚閃避，但卻與貨車相撞，左邊一列玻璃窗連鐵網被撞爛；而尾隨的士的另一部的士亦撞上，釀成4車「串燒」相撞。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警車上有約10名防暴警員，車上亦有大量裝備，警方事後安排另一部車到場，將所有物資移走。"},{"pid":"a95b6a86a39451bd8bb1c02100bc89f9eb5498b4","tid":1810512,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"暴動"},{"pid":"282d9dbe01e7687438f02de10d3f3eff15590c19","tid":1810512,"uid":36248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"2星<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528f3060582fb00484785c85525dc846bae1c617","tid":1810512,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:55:33.000Z","msg":"車上大量裝備<br />\n擺明準備做大茶飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw傷者們快啲去驗傷同寫定不自殺聲明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e5a0df4e213b253dc9d1063d2785c11bdf6a0f","tid":1810512,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"防暴又點<br />\n比你體能飛天<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比架車hi一hi咪又係送院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641dc523e49f375b841f0bbfa2f2c5e2723c84a5","tid":1810512,"uid":228955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:58:36.000Z","msg":"咁都唔死天冇眼"},{"pid":"921cb1164cf319567c187e69f6388dbcad4e7ec0","tid":1810512,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"係咪都比人告，夾佢唔撚死真係天無眼"},{"pid":"6300ad916ac16f8f2313a131bb33e9ac8519f35b","tid":1810512,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"襲警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4597071472b210534202810b9a66fcdeaaa53a8e","tid":1810512,"uid":5715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"的士司機，女乘客GG<br />\n<br />\n實比警賊告到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3095a579dd5b71a26a59eb2c492ea3713794ec48","tid":1810512,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"282d9dbe01e7687438f02de10d3f3eff15590c19","tid":1810512,"uid":36248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"2星<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"平時普通和平遊行都4星<br />\n呢單野起碼6星出軍隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b312e4575696b1d50459e055707019d302807c49","tid":1810512,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{